{"tid":501592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【夕陽工業】灣仔188鹹碟舖被冚 警拉1男子","createTime":"2017-12-17T04:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T13:32:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"47aaf90a6426efd24c0d3cdfed6a033183e6e3db","tid":501592,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171216/large/1513427772_0f28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171216%2Flarge%2F1513427772_0f28.jpg&h=de991527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灣仔警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查後，於今午約5時派員喬裝顧客到灣仔道188號一店鋪，其後在店鋪內撿獲約2850隻懷疑色情光碟，估計總值約8.5萬元。行動中，警員拘捕一名39歲姓張本地男子，涉嫌「發布淫褻物品」及「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」。該名被捕男子現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171216/57590672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57590672&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX39r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=23c73761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F57590672&h=7a437349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171216/57590672</a>"},{"pid":"ae39325d9f4e81b8f95fd7c77cc010f25377a4c1","tid":501592,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"唔識DL?"},{"pid":"810287b15939e51899e38a6a02865c6b85a3b839","tid":501592,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccf47f1d0d2d5e56aa88ac801bc0e79f62ad7ec3","tid":501592,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔識DL?</blockquote><br />\n咩年代啊?仲DL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家轉晒睇線上睇啦<